{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, like all methods in this section, LOO's simplicity allows it to be combined with any model architecture.",
    "LOO's theoretical simplicity comes at the price of huge upfront computational cost.",
    "Training some state-of-the-art models from scratch even once is prohibitive for anyone beyond industrial actors (Diskin et al., 2021).",
    "For even the biggest players, it is impractical to train (n + 1) such models given huge modern datasets (Basu et al., 2021).",
    "The climate effects of such retraining also cannot be ignored (Strubell et al., 2020)."
  ]
}